Package com.flipkart.dao

Interface FlipFitGymOwnerDAO

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitGymOwnerDAOImplement
public interface FlipFitGymOwnerDAO
Interface for operations related to gym owners in the FlipFit application. Provides methods to manage gym owner profiles, gym centers, and time slots.
